Installed minikube ( C:/minkube)
Installed docker ( which inturn installed wls2 ) ( location ? ) 
Started docker from windows startup
Started kumbernetes:minikube.exe start
D:/minkumber>minkube start
Now docker shows that Kumbernetses is running. 
Then from command promopt accessed kubernetes dashboard
D:/minikube>minikube dashboard
Above command launched a browser with kumbernetes dashboard. 

Time to start experiment - hello minikube: https://kubernetes.io/docs/tutorials/hello-minikube/

